body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.  
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of personal information.  
Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand.
The conversation should be at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time and end the conversation.
Return the conversation formatted like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Good day! My name is Paul Parker, and I'm with Prestige Electrician Services. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, my name is Michelle Adams.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hi, Michelle, how can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm having an issue with the product quality of the work done at my house. I'm a bit surprised by this situation.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'm sorry to hear that you're experiencing a problem, Michelle. To better assist you, may I have your account number, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's one two three four five six seven eight.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Michelle. And for security purposes, could you also provide the last four digits of your social security number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, it's nine zero one two.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information. I will look into your issue right away and make sure we address your concerns regarding the product quality.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Thank you, Paul. I appreciate your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: It's my pleasure, Michelle. Thank you for contacting Prestige Electrician Services. Have a great day!
